,"tid":1079432,"uid":151933,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"耶子先最無辜"},{"pid":"5d73032111ed4820b7ca39714216b5cae3efe7e5","tid":1079432,"uid":173179,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57c2a68d7f2ddf36e0f76220258e4d6126dd4a9e","tid":1079432,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a5e23d07a84d12100acb335f399a5f93a5fc14f","tid":1079432,"uid":1121,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FO84Khw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFO84Khw.gif&h=749206bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"派notes俾記者真係鳩噏嘅極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"而家先見到，個女人最後個樣好似好嫌棄份note屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82408e72ac8916a3fe65aebc0159ada818e8f832","tid":1079432,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"雲高爾同摩佬都無異<br />\n一樣唔識贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7763fc2ce437fde496843cbbe78fdfdfa3e0ed14","tid":1079432,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82408e72ac8916a3fe65aebc0159ada818e8f832","tid":1079432,"uid":209890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"雲高爾同摩佬都無異<br />\n一樣唔識贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"完美演繹 五十步笑百步"},{"pid":"29c964ff7b07ed98c0d07d7eae822970f2840409","tid":1079432,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"「我不在現場，但那裏看似改變了，氣氛比以前好。的確蘇斯克查改變了普巴的位置，把他放在更為關鍵的區域。但曼聯現有的一套跟費格遜的不一樣，那是防守反擊。你喜歡這一套，隨你意吧。或許你認為這一套比沉悶的進攻更好看，OK。但對我來說卻不然。」<br />\n<br />\n「蘇斯克查領軍以來只輸兩場，但他要好好處理，畢竟這對曼聯晉級歐聯很重要，在我領軍的時候亦然。但他們能以防守足球取得不敗、稱霸歐聯，亦是摩連奴的功勞，無論你是否接受。」"},{"pid":"0852e8fe466cd1b796578100ef013ae7df550add","tid":1079432,"uid":124891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"92<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f52062fb7fae83e084a073572b336a09c240a4","tid":1079432,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"雲高爾接受BBC訪問時說：「人們相信巴塞是最好的球隊，但實際上以曼城及利物浦比起巴塞更加似一支球隊。兩者當中，利物浦又勝過曼城。在我的哲學來說，最好的團隊應該贏冠軍，<span style=\"color: blue;\">不過我反而希望曼城贏波，因為他們踢的足球風格更加漂亮。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e33b78ee48e1d96f057a25925c5771f43a5163","tid":1079432,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e265953daa8e75ecf19f1c76a5579d71020dd7c","tid":1079432,"uid":182846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:50:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}